Question.Subject: if you use a psp for the internet using your home wireless internet....?
Question.Content: would your parents be able to find out any of your internet history?? if you have only used it on your psp but through your family wireless router?/?
Question.ChosenAnswer: Nope. My brother uses his psp all the time and I can never see his history. And he uses the family wireless router as wll. You kno you can also set up a password for your internet, so no one can go on it and check your history. Hope I helped ;)
